content: I don't know where mathlib's doc is automatically built, but I am guessing it is https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4_docs/actions/workflows/docs.yaml. Enable this workflow to resume scheduled runs." and the latest run was a week ago. Does this mean the doc hasn't been updated for a week?
Thanks, I just re-enabled it and triggered an update! We should have new docs in about 18 minutes.
